24a892064e415244bf82cc3202.webm?t=1728368847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>根据自己的偏好来设置线缆的颜色以及3种不同的布线模式。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >充满真实感的元器件设计</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577620/extras/33e6a66457f304bf51bb11a155a7731a.avif?t=1728368847\" width=610 height=203 /></span><br>通过 Papernoise 的设计，将游戏的沉浸感提高到全新的水平，他曾为 Mutable Instruments、Hexinverter、WMD 等厂商设计元器件模块。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >沙盒模式</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577620/extras/7366f9a28b5ac062f52e547177662435.poster.avif?t=1728368847\" width=610 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577620/extras/7366f9a28b5ac062f52e547177662435.webm?t=1728368847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577620/extras/7366f9a28b5ac062f52e547177662435.mp4?t=1728368847\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>没有任何限制的自由模式，彻底放飞自己的想象力！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自创谜题</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577620/extras/d79d42ef25aa8447b23a9d3382f6a442.poster.avif?t=1728368847\" width=610 height=221 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1577620/extras/d79d42ef25aa8447b23a9d3382f6a442.webm?t=1728368847\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>自己成为谜题设计师，也可以通过创意工坊来体验其他玩家的创作。",
